metadata.name: The outbreak
metadata.description:
—     Three, two, one…      
 
—    Chloe, didn’t we forget anything? 
 
The shining pillar of light ripped the whole room from floor to ceiling. The walls began to shiver, swelling of bleeding hearts. 
 
In unison — The butterfly accepts us, the butterfly hears us, hears everything that happened. The butterfly will cover us with its wings.
